The paper discusses deep learning in medical image analysis and multimodal learning for clinical decision support, which suggests that it could belong to several sub-categories. 

cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on image classification and analysis. 

cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses deep learning techniques. 

cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper discusses clinical decision support, which involves the use of AI techniques. 

cs.MM (Multimedia) is also possible as the paper discusses multimodal learning. 

cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses classification of histological datasets, which could involve information retrieval techniques.
